# Prime Fibernet — Project Context

Migrating from Flutter to React Native (Expo SDK 50, TypeScript 5).
Single unified app for 3 roles: Customer, Officer, Admin.
Backend: Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + Realtime + Edge Functions).
State: Redux Toolkit + RTK Query.
Navigation: React Navigation 6 (tab for customer, drawer for officer/admin).

## Stack

- React Native 0.73+ / Expo SDK 50+
- TypeScript (strict mode) — never use `any`
- Redux Toolkit + RTK Query for all state and API calls
- Zod for all input validation (client and server)
- Nativewind (TailwindCSS) for styling
- Supabase JS SDK 2.38+
- React Navigation 6.x
- React Hook Form 7.48+

## Folder structure

- Screens: `apps/unified-app/src/screens/<role>/<feature>/`
- Components: `apps/unified-app/src/components/`
- API slices: `apps/unified-app/src/services/api/`
- Redux slices: `apps/unified-app/src/store/slices/`
- Types: `apps/unified-app/src/types/`
- Hooks: `apps/unified-app/src/hooks/`
- Utils: `apps/unified-app/src/utils/`
